result.adr_address: 38-40 S Wall Rd, Kowloon City, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 38-40 S Wall Rd, Kowloon City, Hong Kong
result.name: Lemon Thai Restaurant

reviews.text:
There are plenty of good Thai food restaurants in Kowloon City.
On my visit the food was good and prices fair.
The services was slow and clumsy despite the place being only half full.

TWO beers on tap! 
But with a terrible issue: the draft beer was sour and the draft dispensing system dirty. 
(Clean the beer lines with biweekly; replace the kegs when the beer is stale. If the beer goes stale before the keg is emptied check the system for leaks and lower draft beer prices to stimulate more sales.)
Friendly family business with many healthy and delicious options. Ordering is quick and they keep the place tidy. Perhaps the menu could be simplified.

they have a great lunch menu set. 
few options for veg but can request change. 
average looking ambience but good staff. 
taste is good. 
must try.
Authentic Thai food, cooked by Thai Chef, served by Thai waitresses. Recommended for set lunch very reasonable price with a complimentary desert and a drink.
Good food at reasonable prices. Good size.portions

result.adr_address: 香港九龍城城南道38-40號
result.name: 檸檬泰國餐廳

reviews.text:
價格低廉
但食物質素一般
大部份食物含檸檬汁
平時食開西貢嗰間旺x， 原來九龍城有咁好美味嘅泰国菜👍👍👍， 最贊冬陰功湯！ 超good!

帶住少少期望結果真係有啲失望而回。
咖哩椰青軟殼蟹啲軟殼蟹好油，可能炸嘅時候油溫唔夠？
海鮮粉絲沙律好水，而且海鮮只有魷魚。
海南雞預咗冇乜雞味，但係做得唔嫩口，好鞋。
係得個炒飯正常啲。
